a file has been uploaded to the Files area of the EVP-ITC

  File        : /Ann's files/techspracticing010208.mp3 
  Uploaded by : lisbyfarrum <lisby@...> 
  Description : I'm not sure how to interpret this section other than as several technicians practicing transmitting. One says a word and the other gives feedback. I hear this order: "Metal." "Good." "Kettle." "Suck." "Pretzel." "Okay." "Apple." "?" "?" "Practice..you...control..?" At this point, I have decided that I must be losing my mind and can't be hearing what I seem to be, so I ask if anyone can say my name. They ignore me and continue, "Pencil." "Check." "Music...polka."
